overview:
CupidPA is a “romantic” planning service with a mission to improve your romantic life.

Forget spending hours trying to plan a simple weekend, and losing hope with search engines. Imagine what you could do if you have a personal PA for yourself who collects and simplifies your romance planning, all at the click of a button. Information gathered from around the web, structured and ready to access with quick planning templates, and easy calendaring features. Reminders, flowers, gifts all in one place. Thousands of listings covering a wide variety of categories including restaurants, spas, bed and breakfast, wineries, events (music, sports, arts), bars, cafes, parks, city activities and much much more. Whether its spending a day in the city, or hiking at a national park, CupidPA simplifies event search, planning and management of those activities. CupidPA achieves this by leveraging structured content from all over the Web and making it accessible to the user, with advanced user modeling
